46:20.527 --> 46:22.237
♪ Do for love ♪

46:23.489 --> 46:25.574
♪ You've tried everything ♪

46:25.657 --> 46:26.617
Come on.

46:31.038 --> 46:31.955
Come on.

46:34.124 --> 46:36.710
